731252f-a.title: Celebrations - Parades - Municipal events - Rapid Transit Commission.
731252f-a.text:
Celebrations, Parades, and Municipal Events: The Rapid Transit
Commission inspecting sections 7 and 8 of the new subway. This photo taken
on Fifth Ave., at 110th Street.

1900.
